frames.caption: A majestic scene unfolds in a savannah landscape, featuring a powerful humanoid figure with a buffalo head, adorned in ornate golden attire. In front of this imposing figure, a woman in an elegant, gold-colored gown walks confidently, exuding grace and strength. The backdrop of the scene is a vast, open savannah under a warm, golden sky.
frames.description: The scene is set in a savannah, characterized by its open grasslands and sparse trees. The central figures are a mythical humanoid with a buffalo head and a woman in a flowing gown, suggesting a blend of fantasy and elegance. The setting sun casts a warm glow over the landscape, enhancing the mythical and regal atmosphere.

frames.caption: A majestic scene features a powerful humanoid figure with the head of a buffalo, adorned in ornate golden armor, standing behind a regal woman in an elegant golden gown. They are set against a vast savannah landscape with acacia trees and distant mountains under a dramatic sky.
frames.description: The scene is set in a mythical savannah landscape, combining elements of fantasy and ancient mythology. The humanoid buffalo figure and the woman appear as figures of authority or divinity, exuding a sense of power and grace.
